<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Mamindra fo amiko FFPM416</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (Maintimolaly)

[V2]
 Mamindrà fo amiko,
 Ry Jehovah Tompoko !
 Fa miantra Hianao,
 Mamelà ny heloko.

[V3]
 Iza no mamindra fo
 Toa an'Andriamanitra ?
 Iza no Mpanavotra
 Afa-tsy ny Zanany ?

[V4]
 Jeso Kristy no mahay
 Mamonjy ny mpanota
 Izay miankina Aminy
 Ka tsy mandoka tena.

[V5]
 Aza mahafoy ahy,
 Ry Jehovah Tompoko !
 Mamindrà fo amiko,
 Mamelà ny heloko.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>416</hymn_number>
</song>